If True, time over the course of the day will flow from the top of
the chart to the bottom instead of the bottom to the top.</item>
                            <item name="InstanceGuid" type_name="gh_guid" type_code="9">e9df0876-63a0-411b-913c-e3c5c4d6b687</item>
